dialogue.text: Ey! How did... how did you get into my room?! Who are you?
Beep, bop boop. \n(The name's BF.mov. GF.mov and I were dragged here by that video track of yours.)
Right.... so you're a talking, transparent video?                         ...am I dreaming?
Bep bop, boop.\n(Not much of a talker, I prefer singing.)
Is that so? What's your style?
Bop, beep bup?\n(Rapping. Up to some free style?)
Hell yeah, blue boy! I'm kinda sleepy, so lets not get too ahead of ourselves, alright?
